霍华德大学取消迪迪荣誉学位https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-stripped-of-honorary- Degree-by-howard-university-3763849?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=diddy-stripped-of-honorary- Degree-by-霍华德大学Max PilleySat, 08 Jun 2024 15:56:54 +0000 Music NewsNewsHip-hopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3763849 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肖恩·“老爹”库姆斯" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该机构是在一段视频发布后采取这一行动的，该视频似乎显示说唱歌手袭击了他的前伴侣卡西·文图拉(Cassie Ventura)</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-stripped-of-honorary-degree-by-howard-university-3763849">迪迪被霍华德大学剥夺荣誉学位的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肖恩·“老爹”库姆斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sean_diddy_combs-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>霍华德大学是华盛顿特区的一所历史悠久的黑人大学，剥夺了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diddy">肖恩·“吹牛老爹”·库姆斯</a>的荣誉学位。</p><p>此举是在近几个月针对这位说唱大亨的一系列指控之后做出的，这意味着 2014 年授予他的学位已被撤销。</p><p>去年 11 月，针对吹牛老爹的指控达到了顶峰，当时 R&amp;B 歌手兼前伴侣<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cassie-accuses-sean-diddy-combs-rape-abuse-lawsuit-3542013">卡西·文图拉 (Cassie Ventura) 对吹牛老爹的身体虐待和性虐待指控提起诉讼，但吹牛老爹均予以否认</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-and-singer-cassie-settle-abuse-lawsuit-one-days-after-filing-3542698">立案第二天，两人就以“双方满意”的方式解决了诉讼</a>。</p><p>今年5月， <i>CNN</i>获得并发布了一段视频， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newly-published-surveillance-footage-reveals-diddy-attacking-cassie-3757408">显示迪迪据称在一家酒店袭击了卡西</a>。这段视频似乎与文图拉在诉讼中提出的指控相符。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-apologises-for-inexcusable-2016-video-allegedly-showing-him-attacking-ex-cassie-3757559">此后，他为自己在视频中的“不可原谅”行为道歉</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3760505" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3760505" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3760505" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Diddy@2000x1270.jpg" alt="肖恩·“老爹”库姆斯 2023 年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Diddy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Diddy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Diddy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Diddy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Diddy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Diddy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3760505" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年的肖恩·“吹牛老爹”库姆斯。图片来源：Shareif Ziyadat/Getty Images for Sean “Diddy” Combs</figcaption></figure><p>霍华德大学周五（6月7日）表示，库姆斯“在最近发布的视频中捕捉到的行为与霍华德大学的核心价值观和信念根本不相容，以至于他被认为不再值得持有该机构的最高荣誉”。</p><p>该大学还确认将终止以他的名义提供的奖学金，并终止与这位艺术家 2016 年的“礼物协议”。</p><p>库姆斯尚未回应置评请求。</p><p>视频发布一周后，针对这位说唱重量级人物又提出了两项​​指控。第一个<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-accused-drugging-sexually-assaulting-woman-revenge-porn-lawsuit-3548549">指控称库姆斯对乔伊·迪克森-尼尔下药并进行了性侵犯</a>，而另一个<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/third-accuser-files-claims-of-sexual-assault-against-sean-diddy-combs-3548864">指控称库姆斯和歌手兼作曲家亚伦·霍尔在 1990 年或 1991 年轮流强奸了一名匿名妇女和她的朋友</a>，并补充说迪迪在几天后变得暴力。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-hits-back-at-sexual-assault-allegations-enough-is-enough-3554746">吹牛老爹在网上否认了所有针对他的指控</a>，但霍尔没有具体回应这些指控。</p><p>这两起事件都是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-accused-of-sexual-harassment-and-assault-by-music-producer-3593467">制片人罗德尼·“利尔·罗德”·琼斯起诉库姆斯后指控他对他进行性侵犯</a>，举办有性工作者和未成年女孩在场的派对，并强迫他与妓女上床。与此同时，他还被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-accused-of-drugging-and-sexually-assaulting-former-model-3758415">指控对前模特克里斯托·麦金尼(Crystal McKinney)下药并殴打</a>。麦金尼指控他在 2003 年的一场男士时装周活动上对她进行了性侵，先给了她一个“强力”的关节，然后在浴室里对她进行了性侵。吹牛老爹将前者标记为“纯属虚构”，并没有回应对后者发表评论的请求。</p><p> 5 月下旬，吹牛老爹又遭到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-hit-with-another-lawsuit-accusing-him-of-drugging-and-assaulting-college-student-3759456">一名大学生提起的诉讼，指控他在 1995 年至 2000 年代初期间对她下药​​并四次性侵她</a>。他尚未回应<i>《NME</i> 》对此案的置评请求。</p><p> <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/diddy-friends-bad-boy-artists-abuse-violence-1235028178/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《滚石》</i></a>最近的一份报告整理了 300 多名与库姆斯有联系的人的账户，其中数十名同事、合作者和同事深入了解了库姆斯的个人生活。</p><p>纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯一直面临着来自多名市议会成员的压力<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nas-has-been-considered-to-receive-diddys-key-to-new-york-city-3758568">，要求他们从库姆斯手中收回城市钥匙，一些人建议纳斯应该代替他接收这些钥匙</a>。库姆斯去年九月在当前指控浮出水面之前获得了这一荣誉。</p><p><b>如需有关英国性骚扰、侵犯和强奸的帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问</b><a href="https://rapecrisis.org.uk/find-a-centre/"><b>强奸危机慈善网站</b></a><b>。在美国，请访问</b><a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php"><b>RAINN</b></a> <b>。</b></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-stripped-of-honorary-degree-by-howard-university-3763849">《吹牛老爹》被霍华德大学剥夺荣誉学位的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 《摇滚学校》原声带首次登陆流媒体https://www.nme.com/news/music/school-of-rock-soundtrack-arrives-on-streaming-for-the-first-time-3763843?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=school-of-rock-原声带首次登陆流媒体Emma WilkesSat, 08 Jun 2024 11:41:38 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3763843 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="摇滚学院" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>其中包括一首新曲目“In The End Of Time”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/school-of-rock-soundtrack-arrives-on-streaming-for-the-first-time-3763843">《School Of Rock》原声带首次登陆流媒体并</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="摇滚学院" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/School-of-Rock-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-black">杰克·布莱克</a>2003 年音乐喜剧<em>《摇滚学校》</em>的原声带首次登陆流媒体服务。</p><p>原版<em>《School of Rock》</em> <em>（音乐源自电影并受电影启发）</em>专辑收录了演员们演唱的歌曲，包括主打歌和翻唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC</a>的《It&#39;s a Long Way to the Top》（如果你想摇滚） n&#39; Roll)&#39; 以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-who">The Who</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-doors">The Doors</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">Stevie Nicks、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">Led Zeppelin</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ramones">Ramones</a>等乐队的热门歌曲。它还包括一首新歌“In The End Of Time”</p><p>在这部电影中，布莱克饰演杜威·芬恩，一位苦苦挣扎的音乐家，他冒充代课老师“施尼布利先生”，以赚更多的钱并向班级教授摇滚乐。这部电影取得了巨大成功，预算为 3500 万美元，全球票房收入为 1.31 亿美元，后来被改编成音乐剧和尼克频道系列剧，于 2016 年至 2018 年播出三季。</p><p>去年，这部电影庆祝了上映 20 周年，布莱克为此<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jack-black-confirms-school-of-rock-20th-anniversary-reunion-3426356">组织了一次演员聚会。</a>他还表示，只要原电影的编剧迈克·怀特参与其中，他就<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jack-black-ready-school-of-rock-3607581">愿意制作续集</a>。怀特在影片中饰演杜威的室友内德·施尼布利，因创作、编剧和导演 HBO 热门剧集<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-white-lotus-review-3017677"><em>《白莲花》</em></a>而闻名。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7665EvJPat/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-botto